		}
		{
			dependencies: ["25B20970F2E51E30"]
			description: [
				"Great, Now To make sure you continue to have room to put shit until... I dunno, you have enough cobblestone to create a black hole, Make an upgrade base."
				""
				"It's pretty easy, just use some of those levers I gave ya and combine them with a basic chest in a crafting grid."
			]
			id: "20BC0B93A0B52388"
			rewards: [
