		}
		{
			dependencies: ["20BC0B93A0B52388"]
			description: ["You can upgrade your chests by surrounding it in material, the first step is usually copper or iron, copper is cheaper though. As you upgrade it, it can be filled with more and more shit, and you can even make further upgrades, like being able to put multiple stacks in a single slot."]
